        "description": "<p>This plugin adds the ability to create as many site options as you want to customize your theme or your website.</p>\n<h4>Special Features</h4>\n<p>You can easily create many field types such as:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Text input</li>\n<li>Password input</li>\n<li>Textarea</li>\n<li>Checkbox</li>\n<li>Select list / Dropdown</li>\n<li>Multi checkbox</li>\n<li>Radio Button</li>\n<li>Taxonomy dropdown</li>\n<li>Posts list / Custom Post Type list</li>\n<li>Repeatable elements (with drag n&#8217; drop)</li>\n<li>Date field (with date picker)</li>\n<li>Upload field (using media library)</li>\n<li>Slider</li>\n<li>Color Picker</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://remicorson.com\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Developer Website</a> &#8211; <a href=\"http://remicorson.com/support/plugin/easy-theme-options/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Support Forum</a></p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the entire &#8216;easy-theme-options&#8217; folder to the &#8216;/wp-content/plugins/&#8217; directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>Edit includes/options.php file (see documention under settings &gt; Help tab)</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
